-- Olympian Oscar Pistorius Shoots Girlfriend Dead, SAPA Reports
-- B y   C h r i s   P e t e r s o n
-- 2013-02-14T06:30:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-02-14/olympian-oscar-pistorius-shoots-girlfriend-dead-sapa-reports.html
Olympian athlete  Oscar Pistorius ,
dubbed “the Blade Runner” because of his double leg
amputation, shot his girlfriend dead at his house in Pretoria,
the South African Press Association reported.  Police spokeswoman Sarah Mcira said the girl, who was not
named, was shot in the arm and head. Pistorius said he’d
mistaken her for a robber, SAPA reported.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chris Peterson at 
 cpeterson@bloomberg.net  